text: Kismet is a 1931 American drama film directed by William Dieterle and starring Gustav Fröhlich, Dita Parlo and Vladimir Sokoloff.Waldman p.85 It was made at the German-language version of the 1930 Warner Brothers film Kismet. ==Cast== * Gustav Fröhlich * Dita Parlo * Vladimir Sokoloff * Anton Pointner * Karl Etlinger ==References== ==Bibliography== * Waldman, Harry.
